column262: Please give us some thoughts and opinions of this questionnaire when you fill in the questions.

To be aware of the lengh of the survey, the progress bar should indicate the percentage of survey complete, or at least, the questions should be numbered; It will be usefull to have access to the criteria description during the survey, as keywords could be not enough (maybe displaying a link to a page); Instead of given the option of just 4 criteria I would extend to the likely 6.

The questionnaire is too long; giving a N.A. option would fit many statements; the 'neither agree or disagree' option can be confusing; instead of assessing 'sense', 'relevance' could be assessed; adding the statement number/page number/progress indicator could (and even then I'm not sure) help the participant to get to the end of the questionnaire. I hope the exercise is useful for your research, I look forward to discussing it further.
